::Zardus/Reptilica/Bloodystrike::

Zardus reaches the lab, walking into the reprogramming room. The femm was on 
the table, and Zardus sits down in his chair, going back to work. He raises 
his head when he recieves Inzola's message.

The Alliance commander glances down at his comp, glancing over scanner 
reports from the Alliance base.

"Any particular Maximal," he asks Inzola, or will any Maximal do?"
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Reptilica continues working, a bit amused by the behavior of the two new 
bots. Beside him, Bloodystrike puts down a finished weapon, begining to work 
on another one.
